README for gmusicbrowser

REQUIREMENTS

    The following additional features may be enabled by installing the listed
    optional dependencies:

        * Tray icon
            p5-gtk2-trayicon

        * Desktop notifications
            p5-gtk2-notify

        * Gstreamer1 playback output
            p5-glib-object-introspection
            p5-gstreamer1

        * mplayer or mpv playback output
            mplayer || mpv

        * mpg123, ogg123, ... playback output
            mpg123
            ogg123
            ...

